ExecDesc: Netgear URL Filter Cross-Site Scripting Injection
EngDesc: This threat sends a URL request for a file that should be filtered by a Netgear router.  The Netgear router in this instance will filter the request, block the URL, and enter an entry into its log. When the log is later viewed by a user, the Javascript is executed with the privileges of the logged in user.
